The paper discusses the use of deep neural networks (DNN) in safety critical and autonomous systems, which suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of DNNs in computer vision (cs.CV) and control systems (cs.SY), which further supports these categories. Additionally, the paper discusses the verification of DNNs, which could fall under the category of cryptography and security (cs.CR).
